1
00:00:00,001 --> 00:00:10,819
"Thanks to the Studio, Author and others for creating this beautiful work" 

2
00:00:20,050 --> 00:00:20,850
Jiugong,

3
00:00:21,140 --> 00:00:23,210
you don't know at all why you lost.

4
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:25,300
What?

5
00:00:26,210 --> 00:00:27,260
Because

6
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:29,550
you are the only one
who doesn't follow this animation.

7
00:00:32,020 --> 00:00:34,140
(Songhai Antiques Night Market)

8
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:42,310
How much is this?

9
00:00:43,890 --> 00:00:45,390
Thousand-year-old refining furnace,

10
00:00:45,390 --> 00:00:47,350
at a very low price.

11
00:00:48,100 --> 00:00:50,600
Ancient spirit figures, I have them all.

12
00:00:54,210 --> 00:00:55,670
A brilliant insight you have, my friend,

13
00:00:56,310 --> 00:00:58,670
having picked out the treasure of my shop.

14
00:00:59,310 --> 00:01:01,170
Check it out.

15
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:03,520
Look at the finish of the flat,

16
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:04,560
the crystal rust,

17
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:06,890
and the carving,
two dragons playing with a pearl.

18
00:01:07,510 --> 00:01:11,090
This is a genuine dragon slaughtering sword
from the Qianlong years.

19
00:01:12,890 --> 00:01:14,260
It's not bad,

20
00:01:14,260 --> 00:01:16,340
but it doesn't look that old.

21
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:22,680
To tell you the truth,

22
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:23,810
this sword

23
00:01:23,810 --> 00:01:26,260
just came out of a cultivator's cave.

24
00:01:26,890 --> 00:01:27,640
You mean...

25
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:28,390
Are you sure?

26
00:01:28,960 --> 00:01:31,090
A friend of mine asked me to sell it for him.

27
00:01:31,090 --> 00:01:33,260
Besides, I don't want to
keep this hot potato in my hands.

28
00:01:33,260 --> 00:01:33,760
Thunder

29
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:36,590
I have a feeling that you are destined to
meet the sword today.

30
00:01:36,590 --> 00:01:37,890
I'll give you a very favorable price

31
00:01:37,890 --> 00:01:39,210
and it'll be yours.

32
00:01:39,890 --> 00:01:41,340
All right.  How much?

33
00:01:43,310 --> 00:01:44,010
Eighty thousand.

34
00:01:48,890 --> 00:01:50,010
Let's go, Lingling.

35
00:01:50,510 --> 00:01:51,680
Greedy hawkers.

36
00:01:52,590 --> 00:01:54,340
You got it wrong, bro.

37
00:01:54,340 --> 00:01:55,340
I meant eight thousand.

38
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,760
No, eighty.

39
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:58,310
Keep the treasure sword to yourself

40
00:01:58,310 --> 00:01:59,340
to slaughter your dragon.

41
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:39,810
(The Daily Life of the Immortal King
Season 3)

42
00:03:39,810 --> 00:03:42,840
(Episode 5 You Are My Sword)

43
00:03:43,460 --> 00:03:45,960
Under the full moon last night,

44
00:03:46,630 --> 00:03:51,020
the four top swordsmen of Huaxiu gathered
at the highest point of Songhai

45
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:54,770
to have a sword contest
the world had never known before,

46
00:03:55,130 --> 00:03:58,710
in order to decide
who is the No. 1 swordsman on earth.

47
00:03:59,810 --> 00:04:03,340
The last sword contest took place
over a hundred years ago.

48
00:04:03,340 --> 00:04:06,840
The skills of the four swordsmen
have all reached supremacy.

49
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,270
Master Ye from the South is...

50
00:04:09,270 --> 00:04:10,560
All right, all right.  Cut the crap.

51
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,180
Just tell us how they played.

52
00:04:14,460 --> 00:04:17,630
Before the swords
were drawn out of the sheaths,

53
00:04:18,100 --> 00:04:21,130
their force was already felt all over the place.

54
00:04:21,630 --> 00:04:25,880
At this moment, a mysterious swordsman
dressed in white descended.

55
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:29,180
She was wearing a bamboo hat,

56
00:04:29,180 --> 00:04:31,350
a white robe,

57
00:04:31,350 --> 00:04:33,220
with a white sword in her hand

58
00:04:33,220 --> 00:04:36,430
which shone chillingly in the moonlight.

59
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:39,560
The strongest swords of Huaxiu

60
00:04:40,060 --> 00:04:41,760
are all here.

61
00:04:43,260 --> 00:04:44,630
Who are you

62
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:46,220
to interrupt our contest?

63
00:04:47,130 --> 00:04:48,630
Come and fight me,
all the four of you together.

64
00:04:49,130 --> 00:04:50,760
Enraged,

65
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:54,130
the four swordsmen
drew their swords simultaneously.

66
00:04:54,260 --> 00:04:56,880
But in the blink of an eye,

67
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:58,970
a lightning flashed before their eyes,

68
00:04:58,970 --> 00:05:01,470
and all of the four swords were bent.

69
00:05:01,470 --> 00:05:04,470
Instantly, they were all defeated.

70
00:05:06,430 --> 00:05:08,510
You little bugs

71
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:09,850
are not the swords I'm looking for.

72
00:05:10,380 --> 00:05:13,470
Then the mysterious swordsman

73
00:05:13,470 --> 00:05:15,560
kicked the ground gently with her tiptoes

74
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:18,760
and disappeared into the darkness.

75
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:20,350
You made it up, didn't you?

76
00:05:20,350 --> 00:05:22,180
No one can defeat the four swordsmen.

77
00:05:22,810 --> 00:05:24,130
I was telling the truth.

78
00:05:24,130 --> 00:05:25,630
I watched it on live transmission.

79
00:05:26,220 --> 00:05:27,630
Chen Chao.  Wang Ling.

80
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,180
Here.

81
00:05:29,180 --> 00:05:30,430
Come onto the stage for your test.

82
00:05:30,810 --> 00:05:31,470
Coming.

83
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:41,220
Brother Wang,

84
00:05:41,220 --> 00:05:42,600
can't you have a better sword?

85
00:05:43,470 --> 00:05:45,930
If I break your little wood sword,

86
00:05:45,930 --> 00:05:47,220
don't ask me to pay for it.

87
00:06:15,810 --> 00:06:17,760
Li Chao!

88
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:22,060
You said you wouldn't use full force.

89
00:06:24,100 --> 00:06:24,380
Li Chao.

90
00:06:24,380 --> 00:06:25,380
- Jingke,
- Li Chao.

91
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:26,630
- say something.
- Li Chao.

92
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:28,510
Li Chao.

93
00:06:28,510 --> 00:06:30,100
Bent to such an extent.

94
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,680
Guess it has to be reforged.

95
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:39,970
What's the matter?

96
00:06:40,180 --> 00:06:41,560
My Oceans don't obey me.

97
00:06:45,010 --> 00:06:46,130
Look out, Brother Wang.

98
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:51,970
What's going on?

99
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,760
Keep it up, Chief Chen.

100
00:07:08,180 --> 00:07:11,100
How come Brother Wang's sword
has such strong magnetic force?

101
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:14,380
Is it possible that Wang Ling's sword
has reached the awakening stage?

102
00:07:15,350 --> 00:07:16,680
The awaken stage?

103
00:07:17,060 --> 00:07:17,600
Right.

104
00:07:18,260 --> 00:07:20,810
After a spiritual sword has been exercised
by its master for some time,

105
00:07:20,810 --> 00:07:22,180
it will reach the awakening stage.

106
00:07:22,630 --> 00:07:26,010
At this stage, the sword becomes irritable,
aggressive and rebellious.

107
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:29,100
Why are my Oceans drawn to Jingke?

108
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:32,680
That's because a sword at the awakening stage
produces a magnetic field.

109
00:07:33,260 --> 00:07:34,720
In the field,

110
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,810
swords of the same sex repel each other

111
00:07:35,810 --> 00:07:36,630
while swords of different sexes
attract each other.

112
00:07:38,310 --> 00:07:39,600
Was my Li Chao

113
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,810
bent because of that?

114
00:07:41,180 --> 00:07:42,310
What shall we do now?

115
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,220
Our spiritual swords are bent like this.

116
00:07:44,220 --> 00:07:45,470
We cannot go on with the test.

117
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,630
I have an idea.

118
00:07:47,630 --> 00:07:49,430
Why don't you come with me
to Sword Tomb?

119
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,810
Sword Tomb?

120
00:07:54,630 --> 00:07:56,810
Sister Lin,

121
00:07:56,810 --> 00:07:57,930
why did you choose to live here?

122
00:07:58,970 --> 00:08:00,600
I found my sword spirit sister

123
00:08:01,100 --> 00:08:03,380
and we moved back to live here.

124
00:08:04,510 --> 00:08:05,470
Wow.

125
00:08:05,810 --> 00:08:08,180
Why are there so many broken swords
stuck in the ground?

126
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,760
Because this is the tomb of spiritual swords.

127
00:08:11,350 --> 00:08:14,260
Swords that were not properly forged
or were too deformed to be restored

128
00:08:14,260 --> 00:08:15,350
are all sent here.

129
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:18,470
Is this the place where you grew up?

130
00:08:19,350 --> 00:08:20,260
Yes, it is.

131
00:08:20,260 --> 00:08:23,180
That's why I had many materials to
use to learn sword forging.

132
00:08:24,470 --> 00:08:25,380
Don't worry.

133
00:08:25,380 --> 00:08:27,310
My sister will be able to repair your swords.

134
00:08:29,060 --> 00:08:30,630
We are back, sister.

135
00:08:36,920 --> 00:08:37,720
Xiaoyu,

136
00:08:38,130 --> 00:08:39,380
you're back early today.

137
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:42,100
You have some friends with you.

138
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:43,880
Sister,

139
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:46,760
our swords were somewhat spoiled
during our practice.

140
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:48,130
We want you to have a look at them.

141
00:08:50,350 --> 00:08:51,510
Sister,

142
00:08:51,510 --> 00:08:53,470
please see if you can save my Li Chao.

143
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:57,550
Don't stand in the courtyard.

144
00:08:57,550 --> 00:08:58,600
Come into the room and have a seat.

145
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:09,100
It's nothing serious.

146
00:09:09,100 --> 00:09:10,300
The flat is bent to one side.

147
00:09:10,300 --> 00:09:11,220
Straighten it out and it'll be fine.

148
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,720
Sister,

149
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:16,100
please have a look at my Oceans.

150
00:09:17,550 --> 00:09:19,420
What's wrong with all these swords?

151
00:09:20,850 --> 00:09:23,220
It's hard to say.

152
00:09:23,220 --> 00:09:24,760
Check them out and you'll see.

153
00:09:32,300 --> 00:09:34,130
Brother Wang,
what's the matter with your sword?

154
00:09:35,880 --> 00:09:39,170
Oceans, why are you so sad?

155
00:09:43,050 --> 00:09:44,380
I see now.

156
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:46,760
A spiritual sword
reaching its awakening stage

157
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:48,510
is attracted by a sword of
the opposite sex.

158
00:09:49,260 --> 00:09:51,010
But this is the first time
I've seen a sword

159
00:09:51,010 --> 00:09:52,380
with such strong magnetic force.

160
00:09:53,420 --> 00:09:54,220
I don't get it.

161
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:57,130
Brother Wang,
your sword is made from peach wood.

162
00:09:57,130 --> 00:09:58,260
How come it has magnetic force?

163
00:09:59,050 --> 00:10:02,220
A sword at its awakening stage
usually feels anxious and confused,

164
00:10:02,470 --> 00:10:03,850
which tend to make it rebellious.

165
00:10:04,510 --> 00:10:06,050
The magnetic field is the external expression

166
00:10:06,050 --> 00:10:07,050
of the sword's psychological problems.

167
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:10,050
Proper communication and guidance
are needed here.

168
00:10:10,550 --> 00:10:13,720
Do you mean we need to
give a sword psychological counseling?

169
00:10:14,220 --> 00:10:15,050
Anybody home?

170
00:10:19,100 --> 00:10:19,760
Ma...

171
00:10:20,380 --> 00:10:21,130
Students,

172
00:10:21,550 --> 00:10:22,670
what brought you hear?

173
00:10:23,300 --> 00:10:24,100
Brother Zhuo,

174
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:26,050
they are all Xiaoyu's friends.

175
00:10:26,050 --> 00:10:27,220
They are here to
have their swords repaired.

176
00:10:28,510 --> 00:10:29,470
I see.

177
00:10:30,670 --> 00:10:33,170
What does the sword
stuck to your belly mean?

178
00:10:35,470 --> 00:10:37,420
Master Zhuo, let's forget about it for now.

179
00:10:37,420 --> 00:10:39,170
Are you also here to repair your sword?

180
00:10:39,880 --> 00:10:40,670
Yes.

181
00:10:42,220 --> 00:10:43,550
What happened to it?

182
00:10:45,220 --> 00:10:46,670
You must have heard

183
00:10:46,670 --> 00:10:48,880
about the swordsman in white
that recently showed up in Songhai.

184
00:10:49,850 --> 00:10:53,050
She challenged every swordsman
she met to a duel these days,

185
00:10:53,050 --> 00:10:55,130
which seriously affected public security.

186
00:10:55,130 --> 00:10:57,170
The Sever-Star Squad
was deployed to get her.

187
00:10:58,630 --> 00:10:59,670
Then what happened?

188
00:11:03,010 --> 00:11:04,100
It seems...

189
00:11:04,220 --> 00:11:06,510
the way the sword was spoiled is familiar.

190
00:11:07,130 --> 00:11:09,260
What sword does the swordsman in white use?

191
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:12,010
About 1 Chi (1.1 feet) long,
made from peach wood,

192
00:11:12,010 --> 00:11:13,220
very aggressive,

193
00:11:13,220 --> 00:11:14,470
with very strong magnetic force.

194
00:11:15,260 --> 00:11:17,880
During the fight,
it drew all our swords to it and bent them.

195
00:11:24,050 --> 00:11:24,880
Hello?

196
00:11:26,300 --> 00:11:26,920
What?

197
00:11:27,420 --> 00:11:28,720
The swordsman in white showed up again?

198
00:11:29,470 --> 00:11:31,510
Captain, all of our swords are bent.

199
00:11:31,510 --> 00:11:32,760
We cannot fight without swords.

200
00:11:33,550 --> 00:11:34,220
Master Zhuo,

201
00:11:34,220 --> 00:11:35,010
why don't you send us there?

202
00:11:35,300 --> 00:11:36,350
You stay here until your sword is repaired.

203
00:11:37,100 --> 00:11:38,260
But...

204
00:11:38,260 --> 00:11:39,670
you are still senior students.

205
00:11:41,050 --> 00:11:42,220
Don't forget

206
00:11:42,220 --> 00:11:44,170
we fought side by side

207
00:11:44,170 --> 00:11:45,220
and beat the demon race.

208
00:11:46,670 --> 00:11:54,300
(Antiques    Songhai Antiques Symposium)

209
00:11:54,300 --> 00:11:55,630
(Songhai Antiques Night Market)
So weak.

210
00:11:55,630 --> 00:11:58,170
Don't you have even one sword
that can hold up to my strike?

211
00:11:58,800 --> 00:11:59,670
Go get her.

212
00:12:05,170 --> 00:12:05,920
My young lady,

213
00:12:06,350 --> 00:12:08,760
the behavior of this swordsman is weird.

214
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:10,220
Many of our men tried to fight her,

215
00:12:10,220 --> 00:12:11,720
but all their weapons were damaged.

216
00:12:12,300 --> 00:12:13,510
If this goes on,

217
00:12:13,510 --> 00:12:15,220
we won't have enough weapons
in our reserve.

218
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:16,670
Report.

219
00:12:18,010 --> 00:12:19,970
My young lady,
the Seven-Star Squad is coming.

220
00:12:21,420 --> 00:12:22,260
Let's get out of here.

221
00:12:30,260 --> 00:12:31,350
As expected,

222
00:12:31,850 --> 00:12:34,260
you are not the swords I'm looking for, either.

223
00:12:58,420 --> 00:12:59,350
Nice move, Xiaoyu.

224
00:13:01,260 --> 00:13:01,880
Oh?

225
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:04,550
Now comes a sword that doesn't bend.

226
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:13,630
These little cultivator friends
from Faction 60 have great potentials.

227
00:13:14,050 --> 00:13:15,510
However, their skills are not high enough

228
00:13:15,510 --> 00:13:16,510
to hold them up long.

229
00:13:17,380 --> 00:13:19,670
When are you going to
make your move, Master?

230
00:13:20,920 --> 00:13:22,550
Jingke, stop playing around.

231
00:13:23,130 --> 00:13:24,170
Time to fight.

232
00:13:24,350 --> 00:13:25,350
No, I won't.

233
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:33,260
Swords at their awaken stage
are usually rebellious.

234
00:13:33,260 --> 00:13:35,130
Pushing them hard could backfire.

235
00:13:35,970 --> 00:13:37,220
Little brother,

236
00:13:37,220 --> 00:13:39,050
why are you sticking to me?

237
00:13:39,260 --> 00:13:41,050
Because I like you, sister.

238
00:13:42,170 --> 00:13:44,970
Do you know
what kind of spiritual sword I like?

239
00:13:46,420 --> 00:13:48,800
What kind of spiritual sword
do you like, sister?

240
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:50,600
I like powerful swords

241
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:52,350
that can protect others.

242
00:13:53,350 --> 00:13:55,470
I am very powerful, sister.

243
00:13:59,970 --> 00:14:01,600
Songhai Antiques Night Market

244
00:14:05,100 --> 00:14:06,920
Brother Wang, be careful.

245
00:14:07,260 --> 00:14:10,630
(Antiques    Songhai Antiques Symposium)

246
00:14:10,920 --> 00:14:12,720
Anyone else?

247
00:14:16,760 --> 00:14:18,010
Songhai Antiques Night Market

248
00:14:19,010 --> 00:14:21,800
I won't allow you to hurt my sister.

249
00:14:24,510 --> 00:14:25,600
Wait.

250
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:26,510
She is...

251
00:14:27,920 --> 00:14:29,600
All right, all right, Lingling.

252
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:31,100
I know.  I know.

253
00:14:31,100 --> 00:14:32,300
Okay, you win.

254
00:14:32,300 --> 00:14:33,800
It's just a little wood sword.

255
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:34,630
I'll buy it for you.

256
00:14:36,300 --> 00:14:38,630
You seem to have changed your mind, my friend.

257
00:14:38,630 --> 00:14:40,970
I've kept the dragon slaughtering sword for you.

258
00:14:41,130 --> 00:14:42,130
Nonsense.

259
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:43,850
I don't want that sword.

260
00:14:45,760 --> 00:14:47,220
How much is this peach wood sword?

261
00:14:47,220 --> 00:14:48,420
998

262
00:14:48,420 --> 00:14:49,720
Are you crazy?

263
00:14:50,130 --> 00:14:51,920
I'd say this little thing is only worth 9.8.

264
00:14:51,920 --> 00:14:53,970
Be serious, sir.

265
00:14:54,510 --> 00:14:56,420
This is made from genuine Phoebezhennan.

266
00:14:56,420 --> 00:14:57,470
Uncle,

267
00:14:58,600 --> 00:14:59,720
where is the sheath of the sword?

268
00:15:04,100 --> 00:15:05,920
A sword and its sheath make a pair.

269
00:15:05,920 --> 00:15:07,850
You lost the sheath

270
00:15:08,050 --> 00:15:09,350
and now are selling a crippled sword
at such a high price.

271
00:15:12,220 --> 00:15:13,970
Let's go home, Lingling.

272
00:15:13,970 --> 00:15:15,760
I just can't stay any longer
at the stall of a dishonest business.

273
00:15:22,300 --> 00:15:24,050
Finally,

274
