288
00:16:17,220 --> 00:16:19,870
Occasionally I feel depressed.

289
00:16:19,870 --> 00:16:22,720
Occasionally I feel sad.

290
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:27,670
Who knows the weakness behind my smile?

291
